{"tid":2150696,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微軟內部投票 逾6成員工表示反對收購TikTok","createTime":"2020-08-11T05:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T07:28:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6dc7848d6a5aafdc1c2ec66679de6df4a3e1404d","tid":2150696,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國微軟（Microsoft）正研究收購中國字節跳動（ByteDance）旗下短影片APP「TikTok」部分業務交易之際，該公司員工卻感到擔憂，認為微軟收購TikTok是不道德的，且恐讓公司誠信遭到質疑。有外媒引用1份被泄露的微軟內部投票顯示，有63%的微軟員工反對微軟收購TikTok。<br />\n<br />\n《Business Insider》獲得1份被洩露的微軟內部投票資料，指250名微軟員工對「微軟是否應該收購TikTok」進行投票，投票結果顯示，有高達63%的員工表示反對微軟收購TikTok，18%員工表示支持，而另19%的員工回答「不確定」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對微軟收購TikTok的員工稱，微軟收購TikTok的交易不管從任何角度來看，都是不道德的。且認為美國政府強買強賣的事實，將會損害微軟的公司形象，因此主張微軟應該退出談判。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3256468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256468&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lPBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=52afd6c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3256468&h=6a03eae3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3256468</a>"},{"pid":"3fba62fb06bc2346280f1ac949360d1f4e463c2c","tid":2150696,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f56ba76a6aeb779ed70c2a4c1e7c8e3dee0e257","tid":2150696,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"business strategy 都要問員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4ffd424021922266db6812d253688f76690f0c","tid":2150696,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1028e3467bb2e935cbc60426b30e62439b6b